{"tid":2389292,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家幾時先開始發現屋企人變老","createTime":"2021-01-31T19:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T23:41:54.000Z","uid":132174,"like":290,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"b76905ac8fcec621a27e17858569c344723607b8","tid":2389292,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T19:24:30.000Z","msg":"我呀媽上個月突然間話睇嘢好朦<br />\n一check先發現原來有初期白內障+黃斑點病變<br />\n<br />\n早幾日凌晨行出廳 見到佢好夜仲未瞓 <br />\n原來係自己一個睇緊佢隻眼個病啲資料<br />\n個下成個人呆咗 唔知講咩好 唯有輕輕力錫一下佢額頭 同佢講早啲唞<br />\n<br />\n雖然白內障呢啲病好容易有得醫 <br />\n但係突然發現 原來自己都到咗人生呢個階段<br />\n開始有啲驚 呢幾日都冇乜心情做其他嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ac6fb19b7b9d92ea886e2b50a87c8653eac4f5","tid":2389292,"uid":205928,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T19:25:00.000Z","msg":"劍仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668eb3ce2b9c8ac37efd802dfa30b84987fbb22d","tid":2389292,"uid":136738,"like":91,"dislike":1,"score":90,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T19:25:12.000Z","msg":"成頭嘅白頭髮都只可以染 <br />\n染到再黑<br />\n生極都係白頭髮"},{"pid":"598544062621d8c2da7a36fc01425f8e16b46cc7","tid":2389292,"uid":78390,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T19:26:00.000Z","msg":"希望伯母 早日康復"},{"pid":"b1076f1dff483c88b80716dfeb9c0431168fcad3","tid":2389292,"uid":150634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T19:27:14.000Z","msg":"叫埋我一齊行長者通道個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05900688c9fb5c667a41690f91e191dbe2f645a","tid":2389292,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20ac6fb19b7b9d92ea886e2b50a87c8653eac4f5","tid":2389292,"uid":205928,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T19:25:00.000Z","msg":"劍仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T19:28:07.000Z","msg":"仲諗住你哋瞓晒先敢開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" clas